Company Overview of Pursuant Health, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Pursuant Health, a health and wellness company, provides a platform to engage individuals to manage their health and improve outcomes. The company’s health and wellness services are delivered through health kiosks, mobile access points, and online. Its solutions include health risk assessments, incentive management, coaching, and traditional and kiosk-based biometric screenings. The company offers vision, blood pressure, pulse, weight, symptom checking, body mass index, and overall health assessments through health kiosks placed at major retail pharmacies, worksites, and hospitals. Pursuant Health was formerly known as Solohealth, Inc. and changed its name to Pursuant Health in 2015. The com...
Pursuant Health, a health and wellness company, provides a platform to engage individuals to manage their health and improve outcomes. The company’s health and wellness services are delivered through health kiosks, mobile access points, and online. Its solutions include health risk assessments, incentive management, coaching, and traditional and kiosk-based biometric screenings. The company offers vision, blood pressure, pulse, weight, symptom checking, body mass index, and overall health assessments through health kiosks placed at major retail pharmacies, worksites, and hospitals. Pursuant Health was formerly known as Solohealth, Inc. and changed its name to Pursuant Health in 2015. The company was founded in 2007 and is based in Atlanta, Georgia.
