pursuant health inc
Private Company









Company Profile
Sector: Health Care
Industry: Health Care Facilities & Svcs
Sub-Industry: Managed Care
Pursuant Health, Inc. develops and manufactures self-service health and wellness testing kiosks. The Company's products include a self-service vision testing kiosk as well as a self-service health and wellness kiosk for testing blood-pressure, body mass index, and vision. SoloHealth markets its products throughout the United States.




